{"tid":403012,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"負能量 - 覺得人生好苦","createTime":"2017-09-17T00:18:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-17T02:07:12.000Z","uid":136252,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"efddbb1e4404de0ae36f967b592ccd03b98c473a","tid":403012,"uid":136252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T00:18:16.000Z","msg":"失眠左兩晚了 <br />\n覺得人生真係好苦好灰 <br />\n日日就係勞勞碌碌返工，放工就返屋企瞓 <br />\n每個月出糧就俾左一大筆黎住 <br />\n淨番少少，放假話想出去玩都要計過數 <br />\n人地唔知就以為我好孤僻 <br />\n其實原來係窮 <br />\n再唔小心，一諗到將來就仲灰，個生活指數只會越來越差 <br />\n唉，可能1舊舊， 但我只係諗到咩就打咩，唔好意思"},{"pid":"2574845a0754e2c068fc7c606749f4cd7e6264c7","tid":403012,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T00:26:40.000Z","msg":"進修下"},{"pid":"5be532eea974b2a55c390d12d3bbb134309c5e9e","tid":403012,"uid":28781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T00:27:50.000Z","msg":"I know that feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f8601c849c9329cfecc2008daf55332a91de7ae","tid":403012,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T00:28:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6647461cd628eed1aed1bc6b51fb973afd782740","tid":403012,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T00:28:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"be405993e4d1d8441a394c8aec842a186c454ee8","tid":403012,"uid":139828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T00:28:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0bc900c0d73cf38f5c7bb14fca3fb5596a2db34b","tid":403012,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T00:35:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a128b0d630741b71b5a6c7a114c6f746eca17f02","tid":403012,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T00:47:23.000Z","msg":"留名等睇全能連登仔解決在職貧窮<img src=\"/assets/fa